Name: Rollback
About the game: You're A Little Thing That Fell to the bottom. Because you are a little different from other beings. If you go up here, you can get a chance. A Chance to Be Like other Beings. This game is a game that goes up to the top by moving and jumping. Use various objects and collect items while avoiding danger. If there is a blockage in the game, find a place where you can use the acquired items. And this game is not friendly. If you make a small mistake, you will fall to the bottom. But don't be too disappointed or frustrated. Failure is not the end.
